Title: Deep Attention Fusion Feature for Speech Separation with End-to-End
  Post-filter Method
Authors: Cunhang Fan and Jianhua Tao and Bin Liu and Jiangyan Yi and Zhengqi
  Wen and Xuefei Liu
Categories: eess.AS cs.MM cs.SD
